snippet.title: Pakistani Investigation Team to Visit India to Probe Pathankot Terror Attack

localized.description:
Pathankot Terror Attack: 6 member of Pakistani investigation team will visit India to probe Pathankot terror attack. Pakistani authorities have lodged an FIR into the Pathankot terror attack case.
